window.bookSummaryJSON = "Set in 2082, Peter Watts' <i>Blindsight</i> is fast-moving, hard SF that pulls readers into a futuristic world where a mind-bending alien encounter is about to unfold. <p>After the Firefall, all eyes are locked heavenward as a team of specialists aboard the self-piloted spaceship <i>Theseus</i> hurtles outbound to intercept an unknown intelligence.</p>"; 
